rencyservice-1", "currencyservice-2", "emailservice-0", "emailservice-1", "emailservice-2", "frontend-0", "frontend-1", "frontend-2", "paymentservice-0", "paymentservice-1", "paymentservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-0", "recommendationservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "shippingservice-0", "shippingservice-1", "shippingservice-2"], "metric_name": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "request", "response", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"]}, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["currencyservice-2", "shippingservice-2", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "currencyservice-1", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["frontend-2", "cartservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "checkoutservice-1", "recommendationservice-0", "adservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-24T15:10:47Z to 2025-06-24T15:23:47Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-24 15:10:47+00:00 to 2025-06-24 15:23:47+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-1", "shippingservice-0", "recommendationservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["currencyservice-2", "shippingservice-2", "productcatalogservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "adservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-0", "productcatalogservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "checkoutservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "currencyservice-1", "frontend-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["frontend-2", "cartservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "productcatalogservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "checkoutservice-1", "recommendationservice-0", "adservice-2"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "error_ratio", "request", "response", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的日志数据，我已经完成了初始扫描阶段的分析。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"connection refused\", \"transport is closing\", \"transport: Error while dialing\", \"Unavailable\", \"Internal\", \"failed to convert price\", \"could not retrieve currencies\", \"failed to complete the order\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"connection refused 错误，目标服务 currencyservice 在端口 7000 上无法连接，可能是服务宕机或端口配置错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.39.78:7000: connect: connection refused\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"transport is closing 错误，表明 currencyservice 连接突然中断，可能是服务重启或网络问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"could not retrieve currencies: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = transport is closing\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"failed to convert price 错误，currencyservice 无法完成货币转换操作，可能是内部处理异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to prepare order: failed to convert price of \\\"LS4PSXUNUM\\\" to USD\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**关键发现**:\n1. **主要异常模式**: 所有错误都来自 frontend 服务，主要涉及与 currencyservice 的通信问题\n2. **连接问题**: 频繁出现 \"connection refused\" 错误，指向 currencyservice 在 7000 端口无法连接\n3. **服务中断**: \"transport is closing\" 错误表明 currencyservice 连接突然中断\n4. **功能异常**: 货币转换功能失败，currencyservice 无法正确处理价格转换请求\n\n**根因推测**: currencyservice 服务在 2025-06-24T15:10:47Z 到 2025-06-24T15:23:47Z 期间出现故障，导致 frontend 服务无法正常获取货币汇率信息，从而影响购物车和结账功能。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的追踪数据，我已经完成了对异常时间段（2025-06-24T15:10:47Z到2025-06-24T15:23:47Z）的初始扫描分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->currencyservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->currencyservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"CurrencyService连接被拒绝（connection refused），错误状态码14，出现次数超过1000次，是系统中最严重的错误源\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"PlaceOrder操作延迟从正常154721ms增加到异常25856ms，延迟倍数约6倍，严重影响订单处理\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"AddItem操作延迟从正常3982ms增加到异常56165ms，延迟倍数超过14倍，严重影响购物车功能\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HGET操作延迟从正常1740ms增加到异常18656ms，延迟倍数超过10倍，影响缓存性能\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现总结：\n\n**主要根因**：CurrencyService完全不可用，连接被拒绝，导致所有依赖货币转换的服务都出现连锁故障。\n\n**异常传播路径**：\n1. **CurrencyService宕机** → 前端和CheckoutService的货币转换请求失败\n2. **CheckoutService延迟增加** → 订单处理缓慢\n3. **CartService延迟激增** → 购物车操作变慢\n4. **Redis延迟增加** → 缓存性能下降\n\n**最显著指标**：\n- CurrencyService的错误率极高（1000+次连接拒绝）\n- 多个关键服务的延迟增加5-14倍\n- 前端服务出现大量500错误，直接由下游服务故障引起", "metric_analysis_findings": "### 分析结果\n\n根据收集到的指标数据，以下是显著的异常调用链和潜在问题：\n\n#### 检测到的异常指标 (`detected_metric_keys`)\n```json\n{\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"server_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"request\",\n    \"response\"\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n#### 假设列表 (`hypotheses`)\n```json\n{\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常高的 server_error_ratio (37.5) 和 error_ratio (37.5)，以及显著的 rrt_max 增加 (217314.0 -> 29275.0)。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 37.5, error_ratio: 0.0 -> 37.5, rrt_max: 217314.0 -> 29275.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常高的 server_error_ratio (38.67) 和 error_ratio (38.67)，以及显著的 rrt_max 增加 (211058.0 -> 34490.0)。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 38.67, error_ratio: 0.0 -> 38.67, rrt_max: 211058.0 -> 34490.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著的 rrt 增加 (1199.84 -> 5162.83) 和 rrt_max 增加 (1478.49 -> 9476.41)。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt: 1199.84 -> 5162.83, rrt_max: 1478.49 -> 9476.41\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"异常的 client_error_ratio (0.0 -> 33.0) 和 error_ratio (0.0 -> 33.0)。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio: 0.0 -> 33.0, error_ratio: 0.0 -> 33.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著的 rrt_max 增加 (2068.0 -> 8271.0) 和 rrt 增加 (1120.5 -> 3356.62)。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max: 2068.0 -> 8271.0, rrt: 1120.5 -> 3356.62\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 总结\n- **主要问题**：`frontend` 服务的多个实例 (`frontend-0` 和 `frontend-2`) 出现了高错误率和响应时间增加，可能表明前端服务存在性能瓶颈或错误处理问题。\n- **次要问题**：`productcatalogservice-1` 和 `shippingservice-2` 的响应时间显著增加，可能影响整体系统性能。\n- **潜在问题**：`cartservice-2` 的错误率异常高，可能需要进一步检查其依赖服务或内部逻辑。\n\n下一步可以深入分析这些异常组件的日志或追踪数据，以确定具体原因。"}
